        "liquid_ceyTmc": {
          "type": "liquid",
          "settings": {
            "liquid": "4-in-1 Retractable Super Fast Charging Cable\n\nEngineered for efficiency and built for versatility, the 4-in-1 Retractable Super Fast Charging Cable is the definitive charging solution for professionals and tech-savvy individuals alike.\n\nUniversal Compatibility Compatible with Lightning, USB-C, Micro USB, and standard USB-A devices — a single cable that powers your entire ecosystem of devices without compromise.\n\nRetractable Mechanism The precision-engineered retractable design ensures effortless portability. Compact enough for any pocket or bag, it eliminates cable tangling and delivers a clean, organized charging experience wherever you are.\n\nSuper Fast Charging Technology Equipped with advanced fast-charging capabilities, this cable delivers optimal power output to reduce charging time significantly — keeping your devices ready when you need them most.\n\nPremium Build Quality Constructed with high-grade materials and reinforced connectors, this cable is designed to endure thousands of uses while maintaining peak performance and reliability.\n\nDesigned for the Modern Professional Whether in the office, on a business trip, or commuting daily — this cable adapts to your lifestyle, consolidating your charging needs into one sleek, intelligent solution."
          }
        },
        "liquid_KKiNTm": {
          "type": "liquid",
          "name": "Hurry",
          "settings": {
            "liquid": "<section class=\"sale-timer\" aria-label=\"Sale countdown timer\">\n  <style>\n    .sale-timer{\n      width:100%;\n      padding:22px 12px;\n      display:flex;\n      justify-content:center;\n      background:white;\n      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;\n    }\n    .sale-timer__wrap{\n      text-align:center;\n    }\n    .sale-timer__label{\n      font-size:24px;\n      font-weight:500;\n      color:#111;\n      margin:0 0 14px 0;\n      line-height:1.1;\n    }\n\n    .sale-timer__row{\n      display:flex;\n      align-items:center;\n      justify-content:center;\n      gap:10px;\n    }\n\n    .sale-timer__box{\n      width:88px;\n      height:68px;\n      background:#111;\n      color:white;\n      border-radius:6px;\n      display:flex;\n      align-items:center;\n      justify-content:center;\n      font-size:34px;\n      font-weight:700;\n      letter-spacing:1px;\n      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    }\n\n    .sale-timer__colon{\n      font-size:32px;\n      font-weight:700;\n      color:#00000;\n      line-height:1;\n      transform: translateY(-1px);\n      user-select:none;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width:420px){\n      .sale-timer__label{ font-size:20px; }\n      .sale-timer__box{ width:72px; height:58px; font-size:30px; }\n      .sale-timer__colon{ font-size:28px; }\n      .sale-timer__row{ gap:8px; }\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"sale-timer__wrap\">\n    <div class=\"sale-timer__label\">Hurry! Sale ends in</div>\n\n    <div class=\"sale-timer__row\" role=\"timer\" aria-live=\"polite\">\n      <div class=\"sale-timer__box\" id=\"st-hours\">00</div>\n      <div class=\"sale-timer__colon\">:</div>\n      <div class=\"sale-timer__box\" id=\"st-mins\">00</div>\n      <div class=\"sale-timer__colon\">:</div>\n      <div class=\"sale-timer__box\" id=\"st-secs\">00</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n    (function () {\n      const durationHours = 12; // change if needed\n      const endAt = Date.now() + durationHours * 60 * 60 * 1000;\n\n      const h = document.getElementById(\"st-hours\");\n      const m = document.getElementById(\"st-mins\");\n      const s = document.getElementById(\"st-secs\");\n\n      const pad = n => String(n).padStart(2, \"0\");\n\n      function update(){\n        let diff = endAt - Date.now();\n        if(diff < 0) diff = 0;\n\n        const total = Math.floor(diff / 1000);\n        h.textContent = pad(Math.floor(total / 3600));\n        m.textContent = pad(Math.floor((total % 3600) / 60));\n        s.textContent = pad(total % 60);\n\n        if(diff === 0) clearInterval(timer);\n      }\n\n      update();\n      const timer = setInterval(update, 1000);\n    })();\n  </script>\n</section>"
          }
